  "title": "pilaties reformer instructor",
  "description": "<p><strong>We're Hiring: Part-Time Pilates Reformer Instructor</strong><br>\n📍 <strong>Location</strong>: Raffles City Mall<br>\n💪 <strong>Pay</strong>: $30–$50 per class (based on experience) if no experience you have to teach 10hr before goes in to our payrole <br>\n🕒 <strong>Flexible Schedule</strong> – You choose your class times!</p>\n<p>Looking to start or grow your teaching journey in Pilates Reformer? We're offering a unique opportunity to join our vibrant studio at <strong>Raffles City Mall</strong> — <strong>no prior experience needed</strong>. If you’re passionate, presentable, and love connecting with people, we’ll support you in building your class and growing as an instructor.</p>\n<h3>💼 What We Offer:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>A beautiful, high-traffic studio in a premium location</li>\n  <li>Total flexibility – <strong>you choose your time and dates to teach</strong></li>\n  <li>A chance to <strong>gain teaching experience</strong> and grow a loyal student base</li>\n  <li>Supportive studio team and resources to help you succeed</li>\n  <li>Competitive pay: <strong>$30 to $50 per class</strong>, depending on your experience</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>👀 We’re Looking For Someone Who Is:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Presentable and confident — first impressions matter!</li>\n  <li>Great at communication and connecting with students</li>\n  <li>Responsible and committed to growing their classes</li>\n  <li>Able to inspire and <strong>positively influence students</strong> on their fitness journey</li>\n  <li>Passionate about wellness and eager to make a difference</li>\n</ul>",
